reviewText: A good set for Rene Bond fans.  The first has a lot of her but the movie is short and picture quality is not too good.  The second disc is a waste.  Only one scene has picture quality worth watching.
It`s a sexy sexy old timer film, but it gets you horny...hush hush! :)
I enjoyed the work of 8 millimeters of nostalgic films.
For the money I expected a movie, not this rubbish!!! Better luck next time Regards.
